content: I'm feeling pretty good about my Black Friday purchases, but I do want to make sure I'm staying on track with my budget. I've been trying to be more mindful of my spending habits and take advantage of sales whenever possible. Speaking of which, I've also been using cashback apps like Rakuten to earn rewards on my online purchases, and I just redeemed $25 worth of points for an Amazon gift card. It's nice to have some extra cashback to use during the holiday season.
